title: The Emergency Meeting ft. Billy Sorrells & Tyler Chronicles | Ep. 87

description:
Karlous Miller and DCYoungFly are back in the studio!! Plus they brought Billy Sorrells and Tyler Chronicles wit em! They called an emergency meeting to discuss whats going on in these streets with Rob and Blac Chyna, La La and Carmelo, North Korea and more!! This is a must listen! It was so good we had to make a 2 part series! This is part 1 of the 2 part series! Thank you for listening! Enjoy.
